{"type":"article","id":20191,"title":"中共军队的后勤保障怎么样？部队伙食还像以前那么差吗？","uid":50924,"topics":[306,1393,136,1,161,163],"contents":"历史上中共军队后勤就很烂，朝鲜战争很多士兵穿着单衣打仗，活活冻死一堆士兵，伙食也是很烂，李奇微上任后发现中共每次进攻只能持续一个礼拜，俗称礼拜攻势，就是因为后勤只能维持一个礼拜。<br>\n<br>\n一直到新世纪每次抗震救灾，仍然会有救灾士兵用泥水泡面的新闻，然后西北边防战士用雪水煮面，据说现在中共伙食已经大幅提高了，不知道现在后勤怎么样了？还有一点就是，中共为什么那么强调把被子叠成豆腐块？<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/RkOY9S4.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RkOY9S4.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/RkOY9S4.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/cYYYeF7.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cYYYeF7.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/cYYYeF7.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/CNfjeCJ.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CNfjeCJ.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/CNfjeCJ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Osg0Tkw.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Osg0Tkw.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Osg0Tkw.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-06-09","agreeCount":3,"discussionCount":0}